title: Cena addresses the WWE Universe after WWE Money in the Bank: WWE Network Exclusive, July 18, 2021
author: WWE
description:
The Leader of the Cenation shares a message with the sold-out crowd at Dickies Arena in Fort Worth after WWE Money in the Bank went off the air. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.
